WEBVTT

00:01.281 --> 00:03.587
<i>PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i>ON "WAYWARD PINES"...</i>

00:03.587 --> 00:05.224
THERESA,
THERE'S BEEN AN ACCIDENT.

00:05.224 --> 00:06.494
I WANT WHATEVER'S LEFT
OF THE CAR TRANSFERRED HERE.

00:06.494 --> 00:07.864
WE'RE TAKING OVER
THE INVESTIGATION.

00:07.864 --> 00:10.001
I DON'T KNOW WHERE ETHAN IS.
THAT IS THE TRUTH.

00:10.001 --> 00:11.505
ETHAN BURKE
FOR ADAM HASSLER.

00:11.505 --> 00:12.908
MARCY: He's not available
at the moment.

00:12.908 --> 00:15.380
IF THERE'S TIME,
I WANT TO CALL IT OFF.

00:15.380 --> 00:17.752
BUT IT'S DONE, ADAM.

00:17.752 --> 00:18.788
[ GRUNTS ]

00:18.788 --> 00:20.993
HELP!
I NEED A DOCTOR!

00:20.993 --> 00:23.298
WHAT HAPPENED?
THE TRUCK EXPLODED.

00:23.298 --> 00:24.701
PEOPLE ARE GONNA
WANT TO HEAR FROM YOU.

00:24.701 --> 00:26.505
WHAT DOES IT MATTER
WHAT I THINK?

00:26.505 --> 00:29.445
BEN, YOU SURVIVED
A TERRORIST ATTACK.

00:29.445 --> 00:30.916
YOU'RE A HERO NOW.

00:30.916 --> 00:33.788
GIVE ME A READING
ON RUBY'S CHIP.

00:33.788 --> 00:35.292
SHE'S AT HOME IN BED.

00:35.292 --> 00:35.960
SHE MUST HAVE TAKEN
HER CHIP OUT LAST NIGHT

00:35.960 --> 00:37.597
AND LEFT IT IN HER ROOM.

00:37.597 --> 00:39.769
I WONDER HOW MANY MORE PEOPLE
ARE HOME IN BED.

00:39.769 --> 00:41.406
WHAT HAPPENED AT THE FENCE?

00:41.406 --> 00:43.811
TWO GOT AWAY, FOUR GOT TAKEN,
AND KATE'S IN JAIL.

00:43.811 --> 00:45.515
Ethan:
YOUR HUSBAND BLEW UP A TRUCK

00:45.515 --> 00:46.618
LAST NIGHT ON MAIN STREET.

00:46.618 --> 00:47.753
NEARLY KILLED MY SON.

00:47.753 --> 00:49.324
I'M SO SORRY, ETHAN.

00:49.324 --> 00:50.994
SOMETHING MUST HAVE GONE WRONG
WITH THE TIMER.

00:50.994 --> 00:53.466
IT WAS -- IT WAS MEANT TO GO OFF
A-AT THE FENCE.

00:53.466 --> 00:55.671
Alan: I SAY WE JUST KEEP DRIVING
TILL WE HIT SAN FRANCISCO.

00:55.671 --> 00:57.008
THIS TIME TOMORROW,

00:57.008 --> 00:58.410
WE'LL BE DRINKING BEERS
BY THE BAY, MAN.

00:58.410 --> 00:59.680
I CAN'T.

00:59.680 --> 01:02.888
COME ON!
ALL RIGHT!

01:09.035 --> 01:11.507
[ LAUGHS ]
WE MADE IT!

01:11.507 --> 01:12.609
[ LAUGHS ]

01:12.609 --> 01:14.381
[ SNARLS ]

01:14.381 --> 01:16.585
[ SCREECHES ]

01:20.929 --> 01:22.933
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

01:22.933 --> 01:25.338
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

01:32.554 --> 01:34.693
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

01:34.693 --> 01:36.530
KILL HER!

01:36.530 --> 01:37.466
YEAH!

01:37.466 --> 01:40.405
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

01:44.749 --> 01:47.621
[ APPLAUSE ]

01:47.621 --> 01:50.628
Woman: KILL HER!

02:10.841 --> 02:13.815
IS THIS WHAT YOU WANT?

02:13.815 --> 02:17.056
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

02:17.056 --> 02:18.926
DO IT! DO IT!

02:18.926 --> 02:23.035
IS THIS REALLY
WHAT YOU WANT?!

03:13.115 --> 03:15.020
[ SNARLING ]

03:17.992 --> 03:20.064
[ HISSES ]

03:20.064 --> 03:23.906
[ MUNCHING ]

03:33.728 --> 03:36.501
[ SNIFFS ]

03:47.893 --> 03:50.734
[ SNIFFING ]

03:53.606 --> 03:56.813
[ SNARLING ]

03:56.813 --> 04:00.923
[ SCREECHES ]

04:10.712 --> 04:12.549
[ SNARLING ]

04:25.646 --> 04:27.650
[ SCREECHES ]

04:30.824 --> 04:32.194
HEY!
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

04:32.194 --> 04:33.664
WHERE'D YOU GO?

04:33.664 --> 04:34.799
YOU SAID YOU WERE GONNA BRING US
SOME FOOD!

04:34.799 --> 04:36.002
GOD.

04:36.002 --> 04:37.806
I CAN'T TAKE
ANOTHER MINUTE OF THIS.

04:37.806 --> 04:39.143
I'M GONNA LOSE IT,
I SWEAR.

04:39.143 --> 04:40.278
FRANKLIN!

04:40.278 --> 04:41.615
STOP.

04:41.615 --> 04:42.985
YOU'RE MAKING
EVERYBODY NERVOUS.

04:42.985 --> 04:44.354
WELL, SHOULDN'T WE BE?

04:44.354 --> 04:46.292
WHERE THE HELL IS HAROLD
AND THE REST OF THEM?

04:46.292 --> 04:47.696
UH, THANKFULLY,
NOT IN HERE.

04:47.696 --> 04:49.366
MAYBE THEY ACTUALLY
MADE IT OUT.

04:49.366 --> 04:51.337
OR MAYBE THEY'RE DEAD
JUST LIKE US.

04:51.337 --> 04:53.642
WE'RE NOT DEAD.
WELL, WE'RE AS GOOD AS.

04:53.642 --> 04:55.781
THE ONLY REASON WE'RE NOT
IS BECAUSE THE SHERIFF'S BUSY.

04:55.781 --> 04:57.785
IF HE WASN'T BUSY,
HE'D PROBABLY DRAG US

04:57.785 --> 05:00.157
RIGHT OUT ONTO MAIN STREET,
SLIT OUR THROATS, WOULDN'T HE?

05:00.157 --> 05:01.961
ETHAN IS NOT POPE.
HE'S NOT GONNA DO THAT.

05:01.961 --> 05:03.865
YEAH, YOU'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.
HE'LL PROBABLY JUST SHOOT US.

05:03.865 --> 05:05.001
FRANKLIN!

05:05.001 --> 05:06.371
YOU ADD TO THAT THE FACT

05:06.371 --> 05:08.242
THAT WE JUST ABOUT KILLED
HIS LITTLE KID,

05:08.242 --> 05:11.616
YOU THINK THIS GUY'S
GONNA LET US LIVE?

05:11.616 --> 05:13.320
YEAH.
YEAH, I-I DO.

05:13.320 --> 05:15.191
WHAT MAKES YOU SO SURE?

05:15.191 --> 05:16.727
BECAUSE I KNOW HIM.

05:16.727 --> 05:18.097
NO, YOU DON'T.

05:18.097 --> 05:20.303
YOU <i>KNEW</i> HIM.
THE GUY YOU KNEW IS GONE.

05:20.303 --> 05:22.240
NOW HE WORKS
FOR WAYWARD PINES.

05:22.240 --> 05:24.980
HE'S JUST A PATSY,
WORKING LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE,

05:24.980 --> 05:27.151
TAKING ORDERS,
COLLECTING A PAYCHECK.

05:27.151 --> 05:28.856
NO. NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

05:28.856 --> 05:30.793
WE'RE DEAD.
WE'RE DEAD.

05:30.793 --> 05:33.065
YEAH.

05:50.938 --> 05:52.275
EXCUSE ME.

05:52.275 --> 05:54.012
EXCUSE ME.
YOU CANNOT GO IN THERE.

05:54.012 --> 05:55.850
WE'RE LOOKING
FOR THE SHERIFF.

05:55.850 --> 05:57.453
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
YEAH, WELL,
HE'S NOT IN RIGHT NOW.

05:57.453 --> 05:58.990
WELL, WHERE IS HE?

05:58.990 --> 06:01.429
WELL,
IT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

06:01.429 --> 06:03.333
OH, I THINK IT IS.

06:03.333 --> 06:05.905
CLASS ONE OF THE ACADEMY.

06:05.905 --> 06:09.046
WELL, CONGRATULATIONS.
IT'S A REAL HONOR.

06:09.046 --> 06:10.449
IT'S NOT AN HONOR.

06:10.449 --> 06:12.019
IT'S A RESPONSIBILITY.

06:12.019 --> 06:15.226
SEE, WE TAKE THE RULES
OF THIS TOWN SERIOUSLY,

06:15.226 --> 06:16.463
UNLIKE YOUR BOSS.

06:16.463 --> 06:18.067
EXCUSE ME,
BUT ETHAN BURKE

06:18.067 --> 06:20.204
TAKES THE RULES OF THE TOWN
VERY SERIOUSLY.

06:20.204 --> 06:22.076
THEN WHY IS HE
SHELTERING TERRORISTS?

06:22.076 --> 06:24.348
I THOUGHT BLOWING UP KIDS
WAS AGAINST THE RULES.

06:24.348 --> 06:25.918
WOULDN'T YOU SAY SO,
SEAN?

06:25.918 --> 06:27.354
THEY PUT AMY
IN THE HOSPITAL.

06:27.354 --> 06:29.792
I'D SAY
THAT'S AGAINST THE RULES.

06:29.792 --> 06:33.034
AND IF YOU BREAK THE RULES,
YOU HAVE TO BE RECKONED.

06:33.034 --> 06:34.804
THAT'S THE SHERIFF'S DUTY.

06:34.804 --> 06:37.110
WHAT THE SHERIFF
DOES AND DOESN'T DO

06:37.110 --> 06:38.947
IS NONE OF YOUR DAMN BUSINESS.

06:38.947 --> 06:41.052
SEE, THAT'S WHERE
YOU'RE WRONG.

06:41.052 --> 06:46.931
THE FUTURE OF THIS TOWN
IS IN OUR HANDS, NOT YOURS.

06:46.931 --> 06:49.103
AND NOT YOUR SHERIFF'S.

06:49.103 --> 06:51.074
SO, YOU TELL HIM --

06:51.074 --> 06:54.816
IF HE DOESN'T DO
WHAT HE NEEDS TO DO,

06:54.816 --> 06:57.956
IF HE DOESN'T RECKON
THOSE TRAITORS SOON,

06:57.956 --> 07:00.295
SOMEONE'S GONNA DO IT
FOR HIM.

07:00.295 --> 07:03.903
I WILL TELL HIM
NO SUCH THING.

07:03.903 --> 07:05.974
NOW YOU SKEDADDLE,

07:05.974 --> 07:08.447
OR I'M HAVING THE THREE OF YOU
LOCKED UP.

07:08.447 --> 07:09.483
DO YOU HEAR ME?

07:09.483 --> 07:11.153
"SKEDADDLE"?

07:11.153 --> 07:15.329
YOU REALLY WANT TO PUT US
IN A CELL WITH THOSE TRAITORS?

07:15.329 --> 07:18.135
GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

07:18.135 --> 07:20.073
DID YOU HEAR ME?

07:20.073 --> 07:24.416
I SAID
GET THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

07:28.125 --> 07:29.828
COME ON, JASON.
LET'S GO.

07:32.969 --> 07:35.842
LET'S GO.

07:35.842 --> 07:39.316
YOU TELL HIM.

07:45.397 --> 07:46.967
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

07:46.967 --> 07:49.038
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:49.038 --> 07:52.078
ETHAN.

07:52.078 --> 07:54.919
WE GOT THIS
UNDER CONTROL.

07:54.919 --> 07:57.391
UNDER CONTROL?

07:57.391 --> 08:00.197
THEY'VE BREACHED
THE PERIMETER.

08:00.197 --> 08:02.603
WE'RE FORTUNATE
TO STILL BE ALIVE.

08:02.603 --> 08:04.473
YOU HAVE TO STOP THIS <i>NOW.</i>

08:04.473 --> 08:06.511
I WILL.

08:06.511 --> 08:07.514
[ SIGHS ]

08:07.514 --> 08:09.284
I'VE GOT HAROLD IN CUSTODY.

08:09.284 --> 08:11.523
I'LL GET HIM TO TALK AND
FIND OUT WHERE THE OTHERS ARE.

08:11.523 --> 08:13.260
YES, YOU SAID THAT BEFORE.

08:13.260 --> 08:15.532
THEY PUT YOUR SON
IN THE HOSPITAL,

08:15.532 --> 08:17.871
AND NOW -- NOW THIS?

08:17.871 --> 08:20.610
THIS HAPPENED
BECAUSE THEY DIDN'T KNOW

08:20.610 --> 08:24.585
WHAT WAS REALLY OUT THERE,
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T TELL THEM.

08:24.585 --> 08:26.457
NO.

08:26.457 --> 08:27.994
NO, THIS HAPPENED

08:27.994 --> 08:31.066
BECAUSE WHAT YOU'RE DOING
ISN'T WORKING ANYMORE.

08:31.066 --> 08:33.105
THE PEOPLE
OF WAYWARD PINES

08:33.105 --> 08:36.914
ARE FAMILIAR
WITH A CERTAIN WAY OF LIFE,

08:36.914 --> 08:40.421
A WAY OF LIFE
WHERE PEOPLE WHO BREAK THE RULES

08:40.421 --> 08:42.326
ARE PUNISHED.

08:42.326 --> 08:46.235
THEY'RE GONNA DEMAND
RETRIBUTION, RELEASE.

08:46.235 --> 08:47.671
AND IF YOU DENY THEM THAT,

08:47.671 --> 08:50.210
THEN THEY'RE GONNA TAKE THE LAW
INTO THEIR OWN HANDS.

08:50.210 --> 08:52.950
MORE DEATHS WILL FOLLOW.

08:52.950 --> 08:57.627
YOU HAVE TO ACT DECISIVELY
AND SWIFTLY TO STOP ALL THIS.

08:57.627 --> 09:00.399
THIS GROUP -- THEY'RE WEAK.
THEY'RE RECKLESS.

09:00.399 --> 09:03.941
WHY HAVE THEY TAKEN SO LONG
TO DO ALL THIS?

09:03.941 --> 09:05.311
WHY?

09:05.311 --> 09:08.184
BECAUSE THEY'RE DOING
WHAT THEIR LEADER TOLD THEM.

09:08.184 --> 09:11.291
WITHOUT KATE BALLINGER,
THEY'RE NOTHING.

09:11.291 --> 09:13.296
RECKON HER,
AND YOU COULD STOP ALL THIS.

09:13.296 --> 09:14.598
LOOK --

09:14.598 --> 09:17.973
I TOLD YOU
I NEED TO DO THINGS MY WAY.

09:17.973 --> 09:21.581
IF YOU COULD HAVE KILLED
THE EASTER BOMBER

09:21.581 --> 09:24.721
BEFORE HE ACTED,
WOULD YOU?

09:24.721 --> 09:27.193
DON'T MAKE
THE SAME MISTAKE TWICE.

09:27.193 --> 09:29.265
DON'T WAIT
TILL IT'S TOO LATE.

09:29.265 --> 09:32.004
JUST CONSIDER --

09:32.004 --> 09:35.278
ONE LIFE
TO SAVE WAYWARD PINES.

09:57.428 --> 10:00.168
[ GRUNTING ]

10:05.379 --> 10:06.649
SIT DOWN, HAROLD.

10:06.649 --> 10:08.253
I WANT TO SEE MY WIFE.

10:08.253 --> 10:10.391
WE'RE GONNA HAVE
A LITTLE CHAT FIRST.

10:10.391 --> 10:12.195
I'M NOT TALKING
TILL I SEE KATE.

10:12.195 --> 10:15.269
WHAT, ARE YOU GONNA CALL
YOUR LAWYER?

10:15.269 --> 10:16.739
COME ON. SIT DOWN.

10:20.013 --> 10:24.422
YOU KNOW, I THINK IT'S STRANGE,
YOU BEING SO WORRIED ABOUT KATE

10:24.422 --> 10:27.263
WHEN SHE'S ALL COZY
IN A CELL.

10:27.263 --> 10:29.668
ALAN...

10:29.668 --> 10:32.374
THAT'S THE ONE
I'D BE WORRIED ABOUT.

10:32.374 --> 10:34.312
WHAT HAPPENED TO ALAN?

10:34.312 --> 10:36.116
WELL, HE MADE IT
PAST THE FENCE.

10:36.116 --> 10:37.219
HE MADE IT?

10:37.219 --> 10:39.423
YEAH.
ABOUT 50 YARDS.

10:40.526 --> 10:42.397
AND HERE'S ERIC.

10:42.397 --> 10:45.237
OR MAYBE <i>THAT'S</i> ALAN
AND <i>THAT'S</i> ERIC.

10:45.237 --> 10:46.539
IT'S HARD TO TELL.

10:46.539 --> 10:48.411
WHAT DID YOU DO TO THEM?

10:48.411 --> 10:50.281
DOES IT LOOK LIKE
I DID THIS?

10:50.281 --> 10:53.422
HAROLD, IF I WANT TO KILL
SOMEBODY, I'M GONNA SHOOT THEM.

10:53.422 --> 10:54.758
I'M NOT GONNA EAT THEM.

10:54.758 --> 10:57.164
THAT FENCE THAT YOUR FRIENDS
TRIED TO DESTROY --

10:57.164 --> 10:59.168
IT'S THERE FOR A REASON --

10:59.168 --> 11:01.841
BECAUSE THERE ARE THINGS
BEYOND IT,

11:01.841 --> 11:04.146
THINGS A LOT WORSE THAN ME.

11:04.146 --> 11:05.783
THAT'S A LIE.
YOU'RE LYING.

11:05.783 --> 11:07.654
THEN WHAT DO YOU THINK
THAT IS?

11:07.654 --> 11:11.296
YOU THINK THAT'S A LEG,
OR YOU THINK THAT'S AN ARM?

11:11.296 --> 11:15.170
LOOK, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.

11:15.170 --> 11:17.710
I'M EITHER
A-A PSYCHOPATHIC CANNIBAL,

11:17.710 --> 11:21.118
OR MAYBE -- WHAT --
MAYBE I'M TELLING THE TRUTH.

11:21.118 --> 11:22.521
ANY WAY YOU SLICE IT,

11:22.521 --> 11:24.826
I DON'T SEE WHERE YOU HAVE
MUCH OF A CHOICE.

11:24.826 --> 11:28.668
I NEED NAMES OF EVERYONE
IN YOUR GROUP.

11:28.668 --> 11:32.443
AND WHAT HAPPENED HERE
TO YOUR FRIENDS

11:32.443 --> 11:35.450
IS GONNA HAPPEN TO EVERY SINGLE
PERSON IN THIS TOWN...

11:35.450 --> 11:39.659
INCLUDING YOU
AND YOUR WIFE.

11:39.659 --> 11:43.168
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

11:43.168 --> 11:45.440
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

11:45.440 --> 11:47.444
UH-HUH.

11:47.444 --> 11:50.718
NAMES.

11:50.718 --> 11:53.491
[ SIGHS ]

12:39.328 --> 12:41.332
Nurse Pam: THERESA?

12:41.332 --> 12:43.237
How's he doing?

12:43.237 --> 12:46.578
HE'S -- HE'S GOOD.
HE SLEPT THROUGH THE NIGHT.

12:46.578 --> 12:49.585
OH, THAT'S SO GOOD.
THAT'S REALLY GOOD.

12:49.585 --> 12:51.288
AND HOW IS AMY DOING?

12:51.288 --> 12:53.861
OH, SHE SHOULD BE
GOING HOME SOON.

12:53.861 --> 12:56.199
SHE WAS VERY LUCKY.
YEAH.

12:56.199 --> 12:58.338
LET'S FACE IT --
THEY BOTH WERE, HMM?

12:58.338 --> 13:00.475
YEAH.

13:00.475 --> 13:04.484
THERESA,
I DON'T WANT TO FRIGHTEN YOU,

13:04.484 --> 13:07.926
BUT I THINK
YOU DESERVE TO KNOW.

13:07.926 --> 13:10.398
THERE'S BEEN
ANOTHER ATTACK.

13:10.398 --> 13:13.505
SOMEONE DROVE A TRUCK
THROUGH THE FENCE.

13:13.505 --> 13:14.909
TWO DIED.

13:14.909 --> 13:16.311
WHERE'S ETHAN?

13:16.311 --> 13:18.716
OH, NO, HE'S FINE.
HE'S FINE.

13:18.716 --> 13:21.256
HE -- HE WAS LUCKY,
AS WELL.

13:21.256 --> 13:23.327
[ SIGHS ]

13:23.327 --> 13:25.532
THERESA...

13:28.739 --> 13:32.748
I KNOW THAT ETHAN
HAS SHARED WITH YOU

13:32.748 --> 13:34.954
WHAT'S AT STAKE HERE.

13:34.954 --> 13:35.989
MM-HMM?

13:35.989 --> 13:37.459
MM-HMM.

13:37.459 --> 13:39.029
DO YOU BELIEVE HIM?

13:43.272 --> 13:45.812
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO BELIEVE ANYMORE.

13:45.812 --> 13:48.384
GOOD.
THAT'S GOOD.

13:48.384 --> 13:53.295
IT'S VERY IMPORTANT
TO QUESTION THINGS, HMM?

13:53.295 --> 13:56.769
ESPECIALLY RIGHT NOW,
WHEN THINGS ARE SO...BROKEN.

14:00.611 --> 14:04.286
WHY DON'T YOU GO HOME,
GET SOME REST, HMM?

14:04.286 --> 14:05.723
WE'LL TAKE CARE OF BEN.

14:05.723 --> 14:08.930
OH, AND I WOULDN'T TAKE
MAIN STREET FOR RIGHT NOW.

14:08.930 --> 14:10.366
IT'S NOT SAFE.

14:10.366 --> 14:12.906
TAKE BOXWOOD HOME
INSTEAD, HMM?

14:12.906 --> 14:15.779
SEE WHAT YOU FIND.

14:15.779 --> 14:16.915
OKAY.

14:35.991 --> 14:37.762
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

14:45.480 --> 14:47.785
Ethan: PILCHER.

14:47.785 --> 14:49.622
I NEED TO FIND THESE PEOPLE.

14:50.791 --> 14:52.061
EASY ENOUGH.

14:52.061 --> 14:53.631
HAROLD BROKE?

14:53.631 --> 14:55.502
HE GAVE ME 14 NAMES.

14:55.502 --> 14:59.545
WE'RE GONNA NEED SOME HELP
TRACKING THEM DOWN.

14:59.545 --> 15:00.514
OF COURSE.

15:01.883 --> 15:04.121
SHOULDN'T BE HARD.

15:04.121 --> 15:05.725
THEY'RE ALL TOGETHER.

15:05.725 --> 15:07.797
WHERE ARE THEY?

15:10.670 --> 15:12.808
BIERGARTEN.

15:12.808 --> 15:13.977
[ CHUCKLES ]
BRING IT UP.

15:19.423 --> 15:20.960
THEY'RE NOT THERE.

15:25.636 --> 15:27.040
[ Dialing ]

15:27.040 --> 15:32.719
[ Ringing ]

15:32.719 --> 15:34.691
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

15:34.691 --> 15:35.893
BIERGARTEN.

15:52.899 --> 15:55.070
THEY TOOK OUT THEIR CHIPS.

15:55.070 --> 15:56.539
THEY'RE OFF THE GRID.

16:19.759 --> 16:21.563
[ <i>BEEP</i> ]

16:21.563 --> 16:24.470
Man: <i>ANY AVAILABLE NEUROLOGIST</i>
<i>TO E.R. 2.</i>

16:24.470 --> 16:26.140
<i>ANY NEUROLOGIST TO E.R. 2.</i>

16:30.583 --> 16:31.920
Man: 302B?

16:31.920 --> 16:33.958
Woman:
ALL RIGHT, HANG ON.

16:33.958 --> 16:38.534
Woman: <i>DR. ROYA, 6-8-7.</i>
<i>DR. ROYA, 6-8-7.</i>

16:38.534 --> 16:39.938
G.C.S.

16:39.938 --> 16:43.012
HER LEVELS
ARE DROPPING RAPIDLY.

16:43.012 --> 16:44.080
LET ME SEE THAT.

16:44.080 --> 16:45.617
GO AHEAD AND INTUBATE.

16:45.617 --> 16:47.589
ALL RIGHT,
SHE'S RIGHT AT 9.

16:47.589 --> 16:49.226
[ SOBBING ]

16:49.226 --> 16:52.700
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:52.700 --> 16:54.638
WHAT HAPPENED?

16:57.845 --> 16:58.981
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

16:58.981 --> 17:00.551
AMY?

17:00.551 --> 17:02.121
AMY!
BEN, BEN, NO,
YOU CAN'T COME IN HERE.

17:02.121 --> 17:04.593
BUT WHAT HAPPENED?
YOU CAN'T COME IN HERE
RIGHT NOW.

17:04.593 --> 17:06.297
SHE'S HAD A SWELLING
IN HER BRAIN.

17:06.297 --> 17:07.634
WHAT?!

17:07.634 --> 17:08.837
WE HAVE TO PERFORM
A SURGERY.

17:08.837 --> 17:10.741
BEN, YOU CANNOT GO IN THERE.
PLEASE.

17:10.741 --> 17:12.746
NO, SHE WAS IN MY --
SHE WAS FINE!

17:12.746 --> 17:13.748
I KNOW. I KNOW.

17:13.748 --> 17:15.552
SHE WAS LUCID
NOT LONG AGO,

17:15.552 --> 17:18.592
BUT SHE'S HAD AN EPIDURAL
HEMORRHAGE, SWEETHEART, OKAY?

17:18.592 --> 17:21.966
WE'RE DOING EVERYTHING WE CAN.
YOU'VE GOT TO TRUST US, BEN.

17:21.966 --> 17:24.271
PLEASE TRUST US.

17:24.271 --> 17:26.008
[ SOBS ]

17:26.008 --> 17:28.147
[ Voice breaking ]
OH, SWEET BOY.

17:28.147 --> 17:30.652
Shh, Shh, Shh, Shh,
Shh, Shh, Shh, Shh.

17:34.896 --> 17:37.568
START BY CONCENTRATING
ON THE PERIMETER.

17:37.568 --> 17:40.141
WE HAVE TO PRIORITIZE
THE FENCE.

17:40.141 --> 17:42.679
THIS IS GONNA
TAKE FOREVER.

17:42.679 --> 17:44.951
WE'VE GOT
OVER 5,000 CAMERAS.

17:44.951 --> 17:47.123
YEAH, WELL,
WHAT IF THERE'S A BLIND SPOT?

17:47.123 --> 17:50.865
WE'RE GONNA FIND THEM.

17:54.606 --> 17:56.277
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

17:58.282 --> 17:59.284
OH.

17:59.284 --> 18:01.222
[ DRAWER OPENS, CLOSES ]

18:38.640 --> 18:40.377
[ CLATTERING ]

18:59.153 --> 19:01.391
Megan: BEN.

19:03.429 --> 19:07.271
HAS THERE BEEN
ANY MORE NEWS?

19:07.271 --> 19:09.710
THEY WON'T KNOW ANYTHING
FOR A COUPLE HOURS.

19:09.710 --> 19:10.778
OH, BEN.

19:10.778 --> 19:13.050
BEN, YOU MUST
TAKE COMFORT

19:13.050 --> 19:15.724
IN THE FACT
THAT YOU ARE NOT ALONE IN THIS.

19:15.724 --> 19:20.768
THERE'S GREAT STRENGTH
IN UNITY.

19:20.768 --> 19:22.706
IT WILL CARRY US
THROUGH ANY STORM,

19:22.706 --> 19:24.209
NO MATTER HOW FIERCE.

19:24.209 --> 19:25.913
[ RHYTHMIC CLAPPING ]

19:34.399 --> 19:37.774
[ CLAPPING CONTINUES ]

19:37.774 --> 19:40.746
YOU TOLD THEM?

19:40.746 --> 19:41.883
ABOUT AMY?

19:41.883 --> 19:44.255
OF COURSE.
THEY DESERVE TO KNOW.

19:44.255 --> 19:46.927
WE'RE ALL
IN THIS TOGETHER.

19:48.899 --> 19:51.069
BEN, HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ANY MORE

19:51.069 --> 19:53.341
ABOUT OUR CONVERSATION
YESTERDAY?

19:53.341 --> 19:57.117
[ Voice breaking ]
I-I DON'T KNOW.

19:57.117 --> 20:01.092
EVERYONE WANTS TO HEAR
FROM YOU, BEN.

20:01.092 --> 20:03.030
THEY NEED TO.

20:03.030 --> 20:07.039
THIS TOWN,
IT'S COMING APART.

20:07.039 --> 20:09.479
I'M SURE YOU HEARD.

20:09.479 --> 20:11.082
THERE WAS ANOTHER ATTACK

20:11.082 --> 20:12.218
LAST NIGHT.

20:12.218 --> 20:14.490
YES, ON THE FENCE
THIS TIME.

20:14.490 --> 20:17.830
BUT STILL THERE HAS BEEN
NO RECKONING.

20:19.835 --> 20:22.241
YOU REMEMBER -- AS THE FIRST
GENERATION OF THIS TOWN,

20:22.241 --> 20:25.046
YOU ARE A LEADER NOW.

20:25.046 --> 20:27.452
NOT ME.

20:27.452 --> 20:31.094
AND NOT YOUR FATHER.

20:31.094 --> 20:35.003
[ CLAPPING CONTINUES ]

20:54.079 --> 20:58.088
HEY, YOU GUYS MIGHT WANT TO TAKE
A LOOK AT THIS.

20:58.088 --> 20:59.592
[ COMPUTER BEEPS ]

20:59.592 --> 21:03.333
THERE'S SOMETHING GOING ON
AT THE HOSPITAL.

21:05.438 --> 21:07.476
Young Man: BEN!

21:07.476 --> 21:09.580
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

21:09.580 --> 21:12.052
WHERE'S AMY?

21:12.052 --> 21:13.122
WHERE IS SHE?

21:13.122 --> 21:14.492
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

21:14.492 --> 21:16.463
LET HIM TALK.

21:19.370 --> 21:22.443
SOUND.

21:22.443 --> 21:24.949
Ben:
<i>I KNOW THAT YOU'RE ALL WORRIED.</i>

21:24.949 --> 21:27.488
<i>I AM, TOO.</i>

21:27.488 --> 21:31.864
<i>AMY'S IN SURGERY</i>
<i>RIGHT NOW, AND...</i>

21:31.864 --> 21:35.406
<i>THEY WON'T KNOW ANYTHING</i>
<i>FOR A COUPLE MORE HOURS.</i>

21:35.406 --> 21:39.081
BUT I-I SAW YOU ALL,
AND I JUST WANTED TO SAY THAT...

21:39.081 --> 21:42.321
I'M GLAD YOU'RE ALL HERE.

21:42.321 --> 21:44.894
A-AMY'S A GOOD PERSON.

21:44.894 --> 21:50.239
AND -- AND WHAT THOSE PEOPLE
DID TO HER WAS WRONG.

21:50.239 --> 21:52.511
THEY BROKE THE RULES
OF OUR TOWN,

21:52.511 --> 21:55.117
AND THOSE RULES EXIST
FOR A REASON --

21:55.117 --> 21:56.921
'CAUSE WITHOUT THEM,

21:56.921 --> 21:59.593
<i>WE'RE ALL IN DANGER.</i>

21:59.593 --> 22:03.670
<i>I JUST HEARD ABOUT</i>
<i>ANOTHER ATTACK.</i>

22:03.670 --> 22:06.242
[ <i>CROWD MURMURING</i> ]

22:06.242 --> 22:09.649
<i>I JUST WANTED TO SAY THAT I-I'M</i>
<i>SORRY THAT ALL THIS HAPPENED.</i>

22:09.649 --> 22:13.592
<i>AND I'M SORRY THAT MY DAD</i>
<i>FAILED THIS TOWN.</i>

22:13.592 --> 22:16.030
[ SIGHS ]

22:16.030 --> 22:19.037
WELL, WHEN IS YOUR DAD
GONNA RECKON THEM?

22:19.037 --> 22:21.343
HE'S RIGHT.
YEAH.

22:21.343 --> 22:23.380
HE'S NOT GOING TO.

22:23.380 --> 22:24.216
WHY?

22:24.216 --> 22:27.122
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

22:27.122 --> 22:28.292
[ GRUNTS ]

22:36.110 --> 22:38.949
ETHAN.

22:38.949 --> 22:40.987
ETHAN!

23:43.127 --> 23:44.397
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

23:44.397 --> 23:45.599
[ ENGINE REVS ]

23:45.599 --> 23:49.342
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

23:49.342 --> 23:51.346
[ VEHICLE DOORS CLOSE ]

23:55.823 --> 23:57.159
AAH!

23:57.159 --> 24:00.300
Franklin:
ARLENE? WHAT'S GOING ON?

24:00.300 --> 24:02.137
HELP! WE'RE IN HERE!

24:02.137 --> 24:04.342
LET US OUT!
LET US OUT!

24:04.342 --> 24:05.544
Kate: WHAT'S GOING ON?

24:05.544 --> 24:07.282
ARLENE?

24:08.685 --> 24:10.757
[ Dialing ]

24:13.496 --> 24:16.169
KEYS.

24:16.169 --> 24:17.471
GIVE ME THE KEYS.

24:17.471 --> 24:18.775
DON'T -- DON'T --

24:18.775 --> 24:20.311
<i>ARLENE,</i>
<i>DON'T LOOK AT THEM, OKAY?</i>

24:20.311 --> 24:21.615
<i>LOOK AT ME.</i>

24:21.615 --> 24:24.220
<i>THEY'RE NOT GONNA HELP YOU,</i>
<i>ARLENE.</i>

24:24.220 --> 24:26.492
<i>THEY'RE ON OUR SIDE.</i>

24:26.492 --> 24:30.501
WE ARE JUST HERE
TO PROTECT WAYWARD PINES,

24:30.501 --> 24:32.338
TO PROTECT OUR FUTURE.

24:32.338 --> 24:35.446
SO PLEASE...
GIVE ME THE KEYS.

24:35.446 --> 24:36.481
[ SPITS ]

24:36.481 --> 24:37.484
[ GRUNTS ]

24:37.484 --> 24:38.486
COME HERE!

24:38.486 --> 24:39.488
Arlene: NO!

24:39.488 --> 24:42.228
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

24:42.228 --> 24:44.466
COME HERE!

24:44.466 --> 24:45.469
COME HERE!

24:45.469 --> 24:46.237
NO!

24:46.237 --> 24:47.639
NO.

24:47.639 --> 24:50.480
YOU'RE MAKING THIS HARDER
THAN IT HAS TO BE, ARLENE.

24:50.480 --> 24:51.482
PLEASE!

24:51.482 --> 24:53.520
DON'T YOU DARE TOUCH THEM!

24:53.520 --> 24:54.722
OR WHAT?

24:54.722 --> 24:56.560
YOUR SHERIFF WILL THROW US
IN A CELL?

24:56.560 --> 24:58.531
MAYBE GIVE US A HUG?

24:58.531 --> 25:02.206
I KNOW WHAT HE WON'T DO --
RECKON US.

25:02.206 --> 25:05.347
YOU'RE JASON, RIGHT?

25:05.347 --> 25:08.219
JASON HIGGINS.

25:08.219 --> 25:10.291
I KNOW YOU.

25:11.360 --> 25:12.897
I-I REMEMBER YOU.

25:12.897 --> 25:16.305
YOU BOUGHT A TOY SOLDIER
FROM US.

25:16.305 --> 25:19.378
HAROLD -- HE --
HE CARVED THAT.

25:19.378 --> 25:23.287
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN
8, 10 AT THE TIME.

25:23.287 --> 25:25.793
BUT I REMEMBER IT SO WELL.

25:25.793 --> 25:28.632
I REMEMBER BECAUSE YOU WERE
SUCH A GOOD KID.

25:28.632 --> 25:30.369
[ BULLETS THUDDING ]

25:30.369 --> 25:34.378
I DON'T KNOW WHAT LIES
THEY'VE TOLD YOU SINCE THEN,

25:34.378 --> 25:36.483
BUT WHAT I CAN TELL YOU IS,

25:36.483 --> 25:41.328
WHAT YOU'RE ABOUT TO DO,
YOU WILL NEVER RECOVER FROM.

25:41.328 --> 25:44.268
YOU CAN STOP THIS
RIGHT NOW.

25:44.268 --> 25:45.838
IT'S NOT TOO LATE.

25:45.838 --> 25:48.577
Sean:
SHE'S RIGHT, JASON.

25:48.577 --> 25:51.184
WE'VE MADE OUR POINT.

25:51.184 --> 25:53.522
THIS ISN'T ABOUT
MAKING A POINT, SEAN.

25:53.522 --> 25:54.758
THIS IS SURVIVAL.

25:54.758 --> 25:57.197
ARE YOU NOT PAYING ATTENTION
IN CLASS?

25:57.197 --> 25:58.467
YOU DEAF, DUMB, WHAT?!

25:58.467 --> 26:02.609
ONE CRACK IN THE ARK,
AND IT ALL GOES DOWN.

26:02.609 --> 26:03.946
[ BULLETS THUDDING ]

26:09.425 --> 26:11.396
IT'S OUR RESPONSIBILITY.

26:11.396 --> 26:12.766
[ SHOTGUN COCKS ]

26:16.474 --> 26:17.910
[ DOOR OPENS ]

26:17.910 --> 26:20.984
ALL RIGHT. OUT.
OUT!

26:25.561 --> 26:27.465
COME ON!
GET DOWN ON YOUR KNEES!

26:29.503 --> 26:32.242
DON'T LOOK AT ME.

26:35.684 --> 26:37.822
[ KEYS JINGLING ]

26:40.662 --> 26:42.332
COME ON. OUT.

26:42.332 --> 26:43.435
GET OUT!

26:43.435 --> 26:44.971
DON'T DO THIS.

26:46.241 --> 26:47.343
UNH!
OH, GOD!

26:47.343 --> 26:50.952
OKAY, NOW,
YOU COME ON OUT.

26:50.952 --> 26:52.922
DON'T EVEN THINK ABOUT IT.

26:52.922 --> 26:53.792
AAH!

26:53.792 --> 26:55.027
OHH!

26:55.027 --> 26:57.433
WHAT DID I SAY?
WHAT DID I SAY?!

26:57.433 --> 26:59.671
ON YOUR KNEES!

26:59.671 --> 27:01.810
ON YOUR KNEES.

27:01.810 --> 27:04.950
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY...

27:04.950 --> 27:07.991
AFTER ME.

27:07.991 --> 27:10.362
"WORK HARD."

27:10.362 --> 27:11.966
"WORK HARD"!

27:11.966 --> 27:12.968
WORK HARD.

27:12.968 --> 27:13.970
WORK HARD.

27:13.970 --> 27:15.441
"BE HAPPY."

27:15.441 --> 27:16.911
BE HAPPY.

27:16.911 --> 27:18.548
BE HAPPY.

27:20.285 --> 27:23.559
"BE HAPPY."

27:23.559 --> 27:24.728
SAY IT!

27:24.728 --> 27:26.933
Harold: BE HAPPY.

27:26.933 --> 27:28.871
BE HAPPY.

27:30.942 --> 27:34.383
"ENJOY YOUR LIFE
IN WAYWARD PINES."

27:34.383 --> 27:37.491
ENJOY YOUR LIFE
IN WAYWARD PINES.

27:41.967 --> 27:43.537
I LOVE YOU.

27:44.439 --> 27:46.444
[ HIGH-PITCHED WHISTLING ]

27:53.660 --> 27:55.330
[ DISTORTED GUNSHOT ]

27:58.671 --> 28:00.676
[ DISTORTED GUNSHOT ]

28:05.787 --> 28:09.964
[ SOBBING ]

28:17.414 --> 28:18.750
[ GUNSHOT ]

28:20.621 --> 28:21.757
Ethan: DROP 'EM!

28:23.828 --> 28:25.733
DOWN ON THE GROUND.

28:25.733 --> 28:26.969
DOWN!

28:44.141 --> 28:45.477
ARLENE?

28:45.477 --> 28:47.148
[ WHIMPERING ]

28:47.148 --> 28:48.852
ARLENE?

29:09.498 --> 29:10.834
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

29:22.995 --> 29:24.833
[ SIGHS ]

29:24.833 --> 29:27.973
KATE.

29:27.973 --> 29:30.011
KATE.

29:30.011 --> 29:32.951
I NEED YOU TO TALK...

29:35.457 --> 29:37.461
...OR MORE PEOPLE
ARE GONNA DIE.

29:37.461 --> 29:39.933
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

29:39.933 --> 29:42.506
[ SIGHS ]

29:42.506 --> 29:45.079
AND NOT JUST YOUR FRIENDS.

29:45.079 --> 29:47.551
INNOCENT PEOPLE, KATE.

29:47.551 --> 29:48.887
CHILDREN.

29:53.531 --> 29:55.702
THEY DON'T THINK
AMY'S GONNA MAKE IT.

29:55.702 --> 29:58.576
MM. [ SNIFFLES ]

29:58.576 --> 30:00.780
BUT NOBODY ELSE HAS TO DIE.

30:05.559 --> 30:07.830
[ SIGHS ]

30:07.830 --> 30:09.166
HERE.

30:11.805 --> 30:15.113
PLEASE, TELL ME
WHERE THESE PEOPLE ARE.

30:15.113 --> 30:17.919
I'M NOT GONNA KILL THEM.
YOU KNOW THAT.

30:17.919 --> 30:21.227
BUT I CAN'T PROMISE YOU
THAT SOMEBODY ELSE WON'T.

30:21.227 --> 30:25.035
IF I HAVE THEM HERE IN CUSTODY,
THEN I CAN PROTECT THEM.

30:27.107 --> 30:29.646
JUST LIKE
YOU PROTECTED HAROLD?

30:34.892 --> 30:38.266
IF YOU REALLY
WANT TO PROTECT THEM,

30:38.266 --> 30:41.573
YOU HAVE TO STOP
PROTECTING ME.

30:41.573 --> 30:44.212
I CAN'T DO THAT.

30:44.212 --> 30:46.617
YOU HAVE TO.

30:46.617 --> 30:48.656
THERE'S MORE JASONS
OUT THERE.

30:48.656 --> 30:50.660
THEY BREED THEM
IN THIS TOWN.

30:50.660 --> 30:54.001
THEY'RE NOT GONNA JUST STOP.

30:56.172 --> 30:58.979
AND I...

30:58.979 --> 31:00.749
[ SNIFFLES ]

31:00.749 --> 31:04.792
I CAN'T HAVE ANYBODY ELSE DIE
BECAUSE OF ME.

31:04.792 --> 31:07.197
I'M DONE.

31:07.197 --> 31:10.204
YOU HAVE TO PUT
AN END TO THIS.

31:10.204 --> 31:13.345
YOU HAVE TO DO
WHAT PILCHER WANTS.

31:13.345 --> 31:15.282
THERE'S NO OTHER WAY.

31:15.282 --> 31:19.024
IF I DID
WHAT PILCHER WANTS...

31:19.024 --> 31:21.697
YOU'D BE DEAD ALREADY.

31:28.045 --> 31:31.619
SOMEONE'S GONNA KILL ME.

31:31.619 --> 31:34.726
I'D RATHER IT BE YOU.

31:40.907 --> 31:43.914
[ THUD ]

31:43.914 --> 31:46.920
I HEARD SOMETHING.
I THINK THEY'RE HERE AGAIN.

31:56.776 --> 31:58.146
THERESA.

31:58.146 --> 32:00.685
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

32:00.685 --> 32:04.026
THERE'S SOMETHING
I HAVE TO SHOW YOU.

32:06.064 --> 32:08.436
I THINK KATE
SHOULD SEE THIS, TOO.

32:12.144 --> 32:14.382
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

32:19.160 --> 32:22.234
WHERE DO
THESE TUNNELS LEAD?

32:22.234 --> 32:25.039
I DON'T KNOW.

32:41.076 --> 32:42.813
WHAT'S THIS?

32:42.813 --> 32:45.286
Theresa: YOU'RE NOT GONNA
BELIEVE THIS.

32:45.286 --> 32:48.793
IT'S ADAM HASSLER.

32:53.037 --> 32:54.072
[ <i>STATIC</i> ]

32:54.072 --> 32:56.946
[ <i>BREATHING HEAVILY</i> ]

32:59.484 --> 33:02.325
ADAM?

33:02.325 --> 33:05.364
HE WAS IN ON IT.

33:05.364 --> 33:07.034
<i>THIS IS ADAM HASSLER.</i>

33:07.034 --> 33:10.208
<i>IT'S SEPTEMBER 15, 14:20.</i>

33:10.208 --> 33:12.848
[ <i>BREATHING HEAVILY</i> ]

33:12.848 --> 33:14.252
<i>FINALLY --</i>

33:14.252 --> 33:17.091
<i>FINALLY REACHED THE CITY.</i>

33:20.265 --> 33:21.801
OH, MY GOD.

33:21.801 --> 33:24.474
<i>STILL NO SIGNS</i>
<i>OF ANY SURVIVORS.</i>

33:24.474 --> 33:27.481
<i>IT'S JUST ABBIES.</i>

33:27.481 --> 33:29.084
<i>THEY'VE BEEN TRACKING US.</i>

33:29.084 --> 33:30.755
<i>I THINK IT'S --</i>

33:30.755 --> 33:32.425
<i>I THINK IT'S THE SAME GROUP</i>
<i>FROM BEFORE.</i>

33:32.425 --> 33:37.203
<i>SOMEHOW THEY SEEM TO BE</i>
<i>COMMUNICATING WITH EACH OTHER.</i>

33:37.203 --> 33:38.539
<i>I'M GONNA TRY TO --</i>

33:38.539 --> 33:40.511
<i>TRY TO MAKE IT</i>
<i>TO THE OTHER SIDE,</i>

33:40.511 --> 33:42.114
<i>JOIN UP WITH THE OTHERS.</i>

33:42.114 --> 33:43.383
<i>Man: HEY, HASSLER!</i>
<i>AAH!</i>

33:43.383 --> 33:45.855
[ <i>STATIC</i> ]

33:45.855 --> 33:47.259
[ MOUSE CLICKS ]

33:50.867 --> 33:52.438
AND ADAM
WAS JUST LEADING ONE GROUP.

33:52.438 --> 33:54.408
THERE ARE HUNDREDS
OF THESE VIDEO JOURNALS

33:54.408 --> 33:57.883
FROM CITIES
ALL OVER THE COUNTRY, AND...

33:57.883 --> 34:01.324
AND THERE'S
NOTHING LEFT.

34:01.324 --> 34:02.894
[ SIGHS ]

34:02.894 --> 34:05.968
BELIEVE ME NOW?

34:05.968 --> 34:08.841
WHY?

34:08.841 --> 34:12.082
WHY WOULDN'T HE TELL US?

34:12.082 --> 34:15.021
BECAUSE PILCHER'S
A CONTROL FREAK.

34:17.427 --> 34:20.267
WE HAVE TO TELL
EVERYBODY THE TRUTH.

34:20.267 --> 34:22.004
THEY HAVE TO SEE THIS.

34:22.004 --> 34:24.276
HOW DO YOU THINK
WE CAN DO THAT

34:24.276 --> 34:27.316
WITHOUT PILCHER
FINDING OUT?

34:27.316 --> 34:29.354
LET ME WORRY
ABOUT PILCHER.

34:29.354 --> 34:33.096
YOU JUST THINK ABOUT GETTING
PEOPLE DOWN HERE TO SEE THIS,

34:33.096 --> 34:35.969
AS MANY PEOPLE AS YOU CAN
BEFORE MIDNIGHT.

34:35.969 --> 34:37.372
MIDNIGHT? WHY?

34:37.372 --> 34:39.945
WHAT -- WHAT'S HAPPENING
AT MIDNIGHT?

34:41.314 --> 34:44.121
THERE'S GONNA BE
A RECKONING.

34:49.400 --> 34:51.304
[ COMPUTERS BEEPING ]

35:10.882 --> 35:12.585
[ SIGHS ]

35:12.585 --> 35:14.422
WE DID REDUCE
THE SWELLING.

35:14.422 --> 35:16.461
THAT'S ABOUT ALL WE CAN DO
FOR NOW.

35:16.461 --> 35:20.035
JUST HAVE TO...
WAIT AND SEE.

35:27.084 --> 35:29.456
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

35:29.456 --> 35:31.160
YEAH?

35:31.160 --> 35:35.404
UH, SIR, IT'S ETHAN.

35:35.404 --> 35:37.441
HE'D LIKE TO SEE YOU.

35:37.441 --> 35:39.546
WHERE?

35:39.546 --> 35:42.018
HERE.

35:57.587 --> 36:00.093
ETHAN?

36:12.320 --> 36:14.592
I WANT TO RECKON KATE.

36:22.042 --> 36:23.713
RIGHT DECISION.

36:23.713 --> 36:24.982
NO.

36:27.655 --> 36:30.194
IT'S THE <i>ONLY</i> DECISION.

36:30.194 --> 36:34.103
WHEN YOU KILL A SNAKE,
YOU GOT TO CUT OFF ITS HEAD.

36:37.210 --> 36:40.249
KATE'S THEIR LEADER.

36:40.249 --> 36:44.727
SHE BROUGHT THIS
ON HERSELF.

36:50.139 --> 36:53.179
YOU KNOW,
THIS IS YOUR MESS.

36:55.217 --> 36:57.388
I'LL TAKE CARE OF KATE.

37:00.329 --> 37:02.801
BUT AFTER TONIGHT, NO MORE.

37:04.605 --> 37:07.245
THAT'S ALL I WANT --

37:07.245 --> 37:12.222
AN END TO THE VIOLENCE,
A NEW BEGINNING.

37:12.222 --> 37:14.828
WELL, I'M GONNA NEED
EVERYBODY THERE.

37:17.100 --> 37:19.438
EVERYBODY.

37:29.562 --> 37:31.566
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

37:31.566 --> 37:33.637
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

37:37.111 --> 37:40.620
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

37:42.791 --> 37:44.729
YEAH!
KILL HER!

37:44.729 --> 37:49.205
IS THIS WHAT YOU WANT?

37:49.205 --> 37:52.447
IS THIS REALLY
WHAT YOU WANT?!

37:52.447 --> 37:54.284
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

37:54.284 --> 37:55.219
DO IT!

38:03.639 --> 38:05.776
I'M NOT GONNA KILL KATE.

38:05.776 --> 38:08.549
I'M NOT HERE TO KILL ANYONE.

38:10.487 --> 38:12.392
<i>I'M HERE</i>
<i>TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH</i>

38:12.392 --> 38:14.396
<i>'CAUSE WE'RE RUNNING</i>
<i>OUT OF TIME.</i>

38:14.396 --> 38:18.405
<i>YOU'VE BEEN LIED TO...</i>

38:18.405 --> 38:24.285
<i>ABOUT THIS PLACE</i>
<i>AND ABOUT HOW YOU GOT HERE.</i>

38:24.285 --> 38:26.657
<i>AND THERE'S ONE MAN</i>
<i>BEHIND IT ALL.</i>

38:26.657 --> 38:28.594
<i>YOU KNOW HIM AS DR. JENKINS.</i>

38:28.594 --> 38:30.900
[ <i>CROWD MURMURING</i> ]
<i>THAT'S RIGHT -- DR. JENKINS.</i>

38:30.900 --> 38:33.505
<i>BUT HIS REAL NAME</i>
<i>IS DAVID PILCHER.</i>

38:33.505 --> 38:36.479
<i>AND HE HIDES</i>
<i>BEHIND ALL THOSE CAMERAS.</i>

38:40.154 --> 38:41.624
Victor: SIR?

38:41.624 --> 38:43.161
IT'S ETHAN.

38:43.161 --> 38:45.399
HE'D LIKE TO SEE YOU.

38:45.399 --> 38:50.243
WELL, I'M GONNA NEED
EVERYBODY THERE.

38:50.243 --> 38:52.950
EVERYBODY.

38:52.950 --> 38:57.259
<i>HE CREATED THIS PRISON</i>
<i>YOU LIVE IN.</i>

38:57.259 --> 38:59.866
<i>HE WATCHES EVERYTHING YOU DO.</i>

38:59.866 --> 39:02.872
<i>HE TELLS YOU</i>
<i>WHAT JOB YOU CAN HOLD,</i>

39:02.872 --> 39:04.542
<i>WHO YOU CAN MARRY,</i>

39:04.542 --> 39:08.217
<i>AND WHEN SOMEONE HAS TO DIE.</i>

39:08.217 --> 39:10.890
<i>HE USES FEAR AND VIOLENCE</i>
<i>TO CONTROL YOU</i>

39:10.890 --> 39:14.265
<i>BECAUSE HE'S AFRAID</i>
<i>THAT IF YOU KNOW THE TRUTH</i>

39:14.265 --> 39:17.705
<i>THAT YOU'LL SELF-DESTRUCT,</i>
<i>YOU'LL TURN ON EACH OTHER.</i>

39:17.705 --> 39:19.242
<i>BUT CAN'T YOU SEE?</i>

39:19.242 --> 39:20.579
<i>THAT'S WHAT'S ALREADY</i>
<i>HAPPENING.</i>

39:20.579 --> 39:23.719
THE WORLD WE KNEW IS GONE.

39:23.719 --> 39:26.492
IT NO LONGER EXISTS.

39:26.492 --> 39:29.833
YOU DON'T HAVE TO LIKE IT,
BUT YOU HAVE TO ACCEPT IT.

39:29.833 --> 39:32.306
THIS TOWN IS ALL THAT'S LEFT.

39:32.306 --> 39:33.775
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

39:33.775 --> 39:35.646
HE'S TELLING THE TRUTH.

39:35.646 --> 39:39.254
THE ONLY REASON
I'VE BEEN FIGHTING

39:39.254 --> 39:41.292
IS TO FIND OUT
WHAT'S OUT THERE.

39:41.292 --> 39:42.294
AND NOW I KNOW.

39:42.294 --> 39:43.464
I'VE SEEN IT,

39:43.464 --> 39:45.301
AND IT'S THE LAST THING
I WANTED.

39:45.301 --> 39:47.840
I WANTED EVERYTHING WE LEFT
TO STILL BE THERE, BUT IT'S NOT.

39:49.778 --> 39:52.919
HE'S NOT LYING TO YOU,
AND WE CAN PROVE IT.

39:52.919 --> 39:54.723
Woman:
YOU ARE LYING!

39:54.723 --> 39:55.958
SHE'S NOT.

39:55.958 --> 39:59.834
HE'S TELLING THE TRUTH.
I SAW IT, TOO.

39:59.834 --> 40:01.471
SO HAVE I.

40:01.471 --> 40:03.008
SO HAVE I.

40:03.008 --> 40:05.313
SO HAVE I.

40:05.313 --> 40:07.952
Man: SO HAVE I!

40:07.952 --> 40:11.494
Kate: DAVID PILCHER --

40:11.494 --> 40:13.832
HE DOESN'T BELIEVE
WE CAN HANDLE THIS.

40:13.832 --> 40:16.038
BUT WE'RE STRONGER
THAN HE THINKS.

40:16.038 --> 40:18.310
EVEN WITH ALL THESE LIES,
WITH THIS VIOLENCE,

40:18.310 --> 40:20.314
WE HAVE MADE LIVES HERE.

40:20.314 --> 40:22.652
HOW DARE YOU SAY HIS NAME, KATE?
HOW DARE YOU?

40:22.652 --> 40:24.389
AND THIS TRUTH --
IT WILL ONLY MAKE US STRONGER.

40:24.389 --> 40:26.695
WE CAN BUILD A FUTURE HERE
BECAUSE WE HAVE TO.

40:26.695 --> 40:29.033
WHY ARE WE
LISTENING TO HER?

40:31.405 --> 40:33.777
DAVID PILCHER
IS A GREAT MAN.

40:33.777 --> 40:39.725
DAVID PILCHER IS THE SAVIOR
OF ALL HUMANKIND!

40:39.725 --> 40:44.869
HE CHOSE US,
EVERY ONE OF US,

40:44.869 --> 40:47.676
AND THAT IS A GREAT HONOR.

40:47.676 --> 40:50.883
WE OWE HIM OUR LIVES...

40:50.883 --> 40:53.455
OUR TRUST, AND OUR DEVOTION.

40:53.455 --> 40:55.727
WE'RE GONNA LISTEN TO HER?!

40:55.727 --> 40:58.433
SHE TRIED TO MURDER
TWO INNOCENT CHILDREN!

40:58.433 --> 40:59.870
THAT IS NOT TRUE.

40:59.870 --> 41:03.478
SHE TRIED TO DESTROY OUR FENCE,
DESTROY OUR TOWN.

41:03.478 --> 41:04.847
SHE IS A TERRORIST,

41:04.847 --> 41:06.886
AND SHE HAS TO BE RECKONED.

41:06.886 --> 41:07.754
ENOUGH.

41:07.754 --> 41:09.558
[ CROWD MURMURS ]

41:24.893 --> 41:27.632
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH EVERYONE?

41:27.632 --> 41:30.142
WHY ARE YOU ALL
JUST STANDING THERE?

41:32.578 --> 41:36.982
[ CROWD GASPING, MURMURING ]

41:39.118 --> 41:42.521
WHAT HAPPENED TO THE POWER?

42:08.013 --> 42:09.948
[ KEY CLACKS ]

42:31.804 --> 42:33.105
[ SCREECHING ]
